Who doesnt want to won the flippin Batmobile? But which one? I always liked the Tim Burton version best. It is sleek, stylish, yet still has all the goodies you need to fend off psychopathic clowns that keep disrespecting you. It shoots, it has a hard shell. it can release spikey things when someone is following you, it can even drive itself (which is a great option because this thing looks impossible to park downtown). The Batmobile is the dream of every bat boy and bat girl to bat have.
